description: The fund normally invests at least 80% of its total assets in investments the income from which is exempt from U.S. federal income tax (other than AMT). It is an actively managed ETF that invests, under normal circumstances, primarily in VanEck Vectors ETFs that are registered under the applicable federal securities laws and that invest in publicly traded municipal bonds that cover the U.S. dollar-denominated investment grade and below investment grade tax-exempt bond market. The fund is non-diversified.
name: VanEck Muni Allocation ETF
